node.text: 5 weeks since gyms have reopened. 5 weeks of consistent training. My weight has increased from 190lb to 207lb within this time frame. Although the gains (especially strength gains) have been nice, this is the heaviest I’ve ever been and so it’s time to up the cardio!🏃🏽‍♂️💨
